rget level of around two-thirds of its pre-strike size. That compares with the 3,600 that flew the pre-strike version. The unions are backing a buyout bid for Eastern led by <LOCATION> Chicago </LOCATION> commodities trader <PERSON> Joseph </PERSON> <PERSON> Ritchie </PERSON>.
